  "description": {
    "zh": "下午好。 我叫Peacekeeper，Skier向我引荐了你，他说你是一个知道自我价值和忠诚价值的人。不浪费时间了，直接谈生意吧。我需要把一些装备交给某个特定的人。我会给你所需的东西，你的活儿是把它放在海岸线一个特定的地方，放在一个叫……叫什么名字——防波堤的边上。那边有一艘船，放在那儿。都清楚了吗？",
    "en": "Good afternoon, mercenary. My name is Peacekeeper, and you were recommended by Skier, as a man who knows his value and the value of loyalty too. Let's not waste time and get straight to business. I need to deliver certain gear to certain people. I'll give you all the stuff I need to be moved, and your job will be to leave it all in a certain spot - on the Shoreline, next to one of the - what’s it called - breakwaters. There is a boat nearby, and that is where you drop the gear. Is the task clear?"
  },
